data.description: Rarely available Spanish style home in the heart of the desirable Country Club of Miami. This waterfront one story home consists of a large master with ensuite bath, two guest rooms, guest bathroom, open kitchen with eat-in counter, custom tile throughout, formal living and dining room with a separate family room that overlooks  a true entertainers backyard.  Enjoy the recently updated vast under truss patio equipped with electric, beautiful new outdoor ceiling fans and plenty of space for the whole family. Newer roof with boral tile (installed in October 2020 with a ten year warranty that is transferable).  NO HOA, close to major highways, shopping centers, children's park within walking distance and plenty of beautiful outdoor green space to enjoy. Exterior painted in April, 2021
